<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.3">
<l>kuṉṟāl kuḷirmā ritaṭut tukantāṉē</l>
<l>naṉṟā yaperum pukaḻvē tiyarnāṅkūr</l>
<l>ceṉṟār vaṇaṅkun tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>niṉṟāy neṭiyā yaṭiyē ṉiṭarnīkkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One who was pleased, having stopped the cold rain with a hill,</l>
<l>You who stands in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam, where bow those who arrive</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr with Vedic experts of excellent, great fame,</l>
<l>You who is tall, remove the suffering of your servant, me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
